description "Archetype: HK-Series Assassin Droid

Class: Mandalorian
Brief Overview: 
A heavily armored sniper assassin, capable of longterm Wrist Flamethrower usage and equipped to terminate Force users. 

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Dual Heavy Droid Blasters
-- Based on Clone Pistols (3)
-- 10% less FP damage
- Droid Assassin Disruptor (2)
-- 50% more FP damage
-- 15% faster reload
- Frag Grenades (2)
- Sonic Detonators (2)

^6Inventory:
- Portable Assault Sentry

^8Attributes:
- Fast Hacking
- Strength (1)
- Magnetic Plating
- Cortosis (1)
- Blast Armor
- Battery Recharge (2)
- Immune to Mind Trick (2)
- Invisible to Force Sense

^3Abilities:
- Poison Darts (2) ^3[CS1 in Melee]
- Wrist Flamethrower ^3[CS2]
- Radar Scanner (Force Sense 3) ^3[CS3]

~ HK-47: A Hunter-Killer assassin droid constructed by Darth Revan to assassinate targets whom he had deemed threats to galactic stability and peace.
~ HK-50 and HK-51: After finding a hidden HK manufacturing plant on Telos IV, HK-47 reprogrammed the newer models found within to suit his own purposes."